porridge is a 1979 film based on the television series porridge .   it was released under the title doing time in the united states .   all the warders and inmates from the original series appear in the film , with the notable exceptions of lukewarm , blanco , heslop and harris .   there is also a different governor , played by geoffrey bayldon .   the film , set a year before the final episode of the tv series , includes one of the last appearances by richard beckinsale , the actor who played godber .   he died in march 1979 , a few weeks after its completion .